messages.message: :test_tube: diagnose CI test failure with testmo: a few days ago we added the link in instabase CI github status page to testmo in the hope to provide better readability of the CI run results and longer log retention, you can access by clicking the link like the screen shots, testmo also allows you to track the context of a test so if you have a test failed from your CI and wonder if this is not related to your code, you can follow the steps to get a glance on the same test from other PR run, hope this helps
